public VirtuosoBSCModel(com.hp.hpl.jena.ontology.OntModelSpec ont)
Construct the VirtuosoBSCModel class. This class talks to the Virtuoso database. After instantiation, one still needs to call the configure() and connect() methods to set the appropriate configuration parameters and establish a connection.
